Introduction

Template Net Digisol DG-FS4526 SNMPv2

Tested on Zabbix 4.4 with DG-FS4526 running 1.1.0.31 software

May work on other badged Edge-core (https://www.edge-core.com/) switches including models from:

  • Black Box
  • SMC
  • Supermicro
  • TP-link
  • Transition networks

Created by full clone of Template Net Digisol DG-GS4524 SNMPv2 then:

  • Items: added
    • Model name

Installation

Administration > General > Macros: SNMP_COMMUNITY

Download the file (link below).

Configuration > Templates > Import > browse to the downloaded file > Import

Configure a host > Templates > Link new templates > search for Template Net Digisol DG-FS4526 SNMPv2 > Add

Bugs

None identified
